definitions.definition: Any of various edible fish , formerly species of the genus Tilapia , but now placed in other cichlid genera (such as Oreochromis ), native to Africa and the Middle East but cultivated worldwide .
A fishy ( resembling a cisgender woman ) drag queen ; a drag queen who could pass for a woman, as opposed to one who is exaggeratedly feminine.
